longBusinessSummary: OTRS AG, together with its subsidiaries, provides OTRS service management software. The company offers OTRS, a ticket and process management system that allows service management professionals in any industry to keep pace with today's results-driven business environment; Storm, a cyber-security management software; and Control, a solution to implement an ISMS systems. It also provides OTRS On-Premise solution and service desk software. The company offers its OTRS products in 40 different languages worldwide. OTRS AG was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Oberursel, Germany.
